{"tid":41912,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家千其唔好受依條友影響！！！","createTime":"2016-12-16T09:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T02:22:20.000Z","uid":5190,"like":64,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b2dfbaabab84dfdc6b687c256c435ad40088913","tid":41912,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:00:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TZYgeX0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTZYgeX0.jpg&h=fb783d08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會員 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>為什麼你這麼熟練</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n成篇野口口聲聲話返高登文化 謝絕舊高登仔<br />\n成件事根本就係想引我地食班舊高登已過檔會員出黎話高登有咩好文化 係想我地覺得依到已經比搞衰 從我地口中講高登文化有幾好 令我地有個錯覺係高登好過依到<br />\n大家千其唔好撚信依條友 我同佢理論過 佢又一味話你死全家 咩反駁都無做 淨係搞嬲你 其實係想你覺得連登變撚到咁樣 不如返去啦依種諗法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又係一個死打手<br />\n連登各位巴打頂住 佢地依家用誘餌法搞鳩我地 要企定 堅持自己要一直留係連登嘅信念<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打手 屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"5a87ca1fff7f793db96aff982bbb452ca228dce1","tid":41912,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:02:19.000Z","msg":"有啲錯字 打得太心急 唔好意思"},{"pid":"102aa4bff0486b6d0ab09f00d8ce34fb1895348f","tid":41912,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d51e6ee7e5653c9d06bf4d75fa4dc2d4cb91dfe","tid":41912,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d320ad94d560e3552f6337bd78c2d004b8f350","tid":41912,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5deea9a34e943e831aadf37eebbbeb4f7d82e3","tid":41912,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:15:53.000Z","ms